            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_85gc' title='Col. 85GC &mdash; HL Deb 14 March 2002 vol 632 c85GC' name='column_85gc' href='#column_85gc' rel='bookmark'>85GC</a>
            time, but this is not the normal procedure in tribunals; it is only when there is some exceptional reason for thinking that costs should be awarded.</p><p>
