      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0632P0-03150'>
        <a name='S5LV0632P0_20020314_GCR_105'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-andrew-mcintosh' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0632P0_20020314_GCR_105' title='Link to this speech by Mr Andrew McIntosh' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
